<item>
            <title>[LUDOC-481] OSS memory requirements do not add up (section 5.5.3.1)</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-481</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In section 5.5.3.1, a set of requirements and size are listed. The total of all the size listed in the table is 56672 MB. The text immediately after says &quot; Therefore, for a non-failover configuration, the minimum RAM would be about 32 GB for an OSS node with eight OSTs&quot; This statement does not match the table at all. Can we get some clarity? &lt;/p&gt;</description>
